）是<span style=\"color: red;\">中華人民共和國一家從事資訊與通訊解決方案的供應商<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>，總部位於廣東省深圳市。華為於1987年註冊成立，業務範圍涉及電信網路、企業網路、消費者和雲端運算。"},{"pid":"882514a6bd9fb934528c196bf9c352757af2b9d3","tid":169614,"uid":43296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T18:13:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"555beab1d07927a0c24da605e1efc34b3b5636ef","tid":169614,"uid":83518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T03:31:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知係頻譜定係咩問題<br />\n但地鐵站入面SMT收得好D既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsmartone負責幫地鐵鋪線,唔知關唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe80308f7c117ab19705ae4e956736a0a79b49d1","tid":169614,"uid":13719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T03:54:48.000Z","msg":"CSL放工時間塔地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtween 用緊csl<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001035d756113480a95294730d633790d74e3027","tid":169614,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T08:15:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上下載係得CSL先係最好 <br />\nSMT套野同華為套野對比完全垃圾</blockquote><br />\n55"}]}